{"tid":973938,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"消失的選項","createTime":"2019-01-08T13:34:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-08T13:34:58.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1ce42b256591d3a234310e0909b229e68baea91d","tid":973938,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T13:34:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/陳也/daily/article/20190108/20585859\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190108%2F20585859&d=YzhzPCpgBYRVwF9Kd3lPzrDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=a222013c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190108%2F20585859&h=8a94493d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/陳也/daily/article/20190108/20585859</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年01月08日 <br />\n<br />\n消失的選項 - 陳也<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20190108/large/e8813a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20190108%2Flarge%2Fe8813a.jpg&h=710317fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n讓世界上一道菜消失。<br />\n<br />\n蔡瀾選火鍋，葉一南揀自助餐。兩樣都係我的頂頭熱門心水，極希望它們永久湮滅。再下一城，火鍋與自助餐之後，我會叮走過年時阿茂阿壽都會推出而且送到上門的偽盆菜。<br />\n<br />\n其他人消失的menu選項，會點叮？<br />\n<br />\n林鄭奶媽念念不忘，肯定最想滅絕薯片！<br />\n<br />\n張建樽被預先張揚的換馬傳聞嚇到鼻哥窿無肉，所以最想咖喱魷魚隨中華白海豚一起消失。<br />\n<br />\n鄭白眼雖然有個特大僭建地牢避風頭，但崩口人忌崩口碗，至鬼憎，燉冬菇。<br />\n<br />\n689唔使喺fb宣揚，係人都知廉記咖啡唔係佢杯茶，廉啡消失，就不會有人質問五千萬可以沖出幾多杯絲襪奶茶。<br />\n<br />\n楊教局針對廣東話教學，長遠而言必然趕盡冇乜用的廣東菜，學校飯堂以煲冬瓜取替。<br />\n<br />\n蔡英文總統不接受一國兩制，高姿態下令把豬骨湯世世代代趕出寶島。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普冇文化，堅定不移要美國優先，對豬雜雞雜牛雜通通說Fxxx！落閘！  <br />\n<br />\n陳也 <br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n信心危機 (尊子)"}]}